node.text: Sigh 😔 Meet 17 yr old Kaylan…Last year November, she was attacked and beaten damn near to death by a group of females simply for being in the wrong place at the wrong time 😞 She has not only lost her memory but she is battling liver infection and numerous other infections and her heart has stopped beating on at-least 7 different occasions but God keeps bringing her back …🥺 I do not know Kaylan guys …I was just moved by the story and saw her mom pleading for help because all the progress Kaylan has made is through the door because she is now back to square 1 due to lack of resources 🥺She’s been in one of Jamaica’s hospital for 9 months but the resources needed to save her life just aren’t there 🥺 If you know how we can get her better help in Jamaica please reach out to her mom @venbuckley . If not you can donate whatever you can so that we can get her here for better treatment 🙏🏾 Her moms page is @venbuckley and Kaylans gofundme is in her moms bio.
